metadata.name: CAT WIZARD
metadata.description:
CAT WIZARD , created by ML moe
Size 2048x2048 mp4
Inspired by the cats I have, plus my love of magic.
It made a story when my cat became a wizard. How will it be?
Contrasting colors add a playful touch to this piece.
**The bidder will receive a JPG file as a gift <3**
I draw with i pad and animate it using AE program.
I hope you like my work. Thank you. Enjoy.
